  description="Terms of Service for Lumecon and its family of products: Local Economic Impact, Tribal Economic Impact, and Global Economic Impact. Covers software, subscriptions, advisory, and Cedar AI usage."
  canonical="https://lumecon.ai/terms"
  keywords="Lumecon terms of service, economic impact analysis terms, Cedar AI terms, Lumecon legal, tribal economic impact terms, IMPLAN, RIMS II, REMI, Cornell University"
>
  <h1 class="hl-block hl-block--green">Terms of Service</h1>
  <div class="date">Being prepared by legal counsel</div>
  <p>The Terms of Service for Lumecon and its family of products (Local Economic Impact, Tribal Economic Impact, and Global Economic Impact) are being prepared.</p>
  <p>These terms will govern use of all Lumecon services, software, annual subscriptions, bespoke advisory, and associated websites, including the Cedar&trade; AI assistant.</p>
  <p>Lumecon, We luminate economies, Cedar, Local Economic Impact, Tribal Economic Impact, and Global Economic Impact are trademarks of {site.legalEntity}. Lumecon&rsquo;s technology is patent pending and remains the exclusive intellectual property of the company.</p>
  <div class="note"><strong>Counsel:</strong> {site.counsel}<br>Contact: <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`} class="note-link">{site.email}</a></div>
</LegalLayout>
